                "meta": {}
            }

+ Response 500 (application/json)
            
            {
                "status": "FAIL",
                "data": {},
                "errors": [
                    {
                        "code": "server.error.internal",
                        "message": "An internal error while processing request."
                    }
                ],
                "meta": {}
            }

`Note`: When the error code returned from the sales force system while confirming the CHI appointment details is either of 1,2,3 and 9 values the above error message will be returned from the endpoint.

